│ with the APInt Offset1 without truncation.\n\n4. Proposed Edit Point(s):\n-   │
│ File: llvm/lib/Transforms/AggressiveInstCombine/AggressiveInstCombine.cpp\n-  │
│ Lines: 802–808\n- Change the creation of the index constant for PtrAdd to use │
│ the DL-derived index type instead of hardcoded i32.\n\nSuggested replacement  │
│ for those lines:\n\n  // Use the correct DL-based index type for pointer      │
