│ integer type matching the pointer’s indexing width (respecting datalayout     │
│ like e-n64).\n- Avoid Builder.getInt32 here; using i32 caused truncation and  │
│ incorrect negative index.\n\nIf CreatePtrAdd requires the index to match the  │
